        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2017-04-05 07:03:38.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAs I understand it the problem is that you have this hardcoded 1.0.0 in this pom, but in the others it's 1.0.0-SNAPSHOT.\n\nSo if you try to build just this branch this as is it fails as you haven't built the correct dependency. \n\nFor me we should either remove this hardcoded 1.0.0 and move it to 1.0.0-SNAPSHOT and leave the versioning to the versions plugin or hardcode 1.0.0 everywhere.\n\nI chose to remove the hardcoded 1.0.0 because it makes it much more easier if you want to build a snapshot of this branch in the future.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      }
    ]
  }
